.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, water
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, doctor
2 different pets are kept: frog, goat
The people have 2 different hobbies: gardening, fishing
1. the doctor is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | water    |
| Job         | doctor        | designer |
| Pet         | frog          | goat     |
| Hobby   | gardening        | fishing     |

 